SubString.CExoString: This hunched creature is fashioned from dark stone. From the corner of your eye it almost seems to move, but when you turn to face it, all is still.
This hunched creature is fashioned from dark stone. From the corner of your eye it almost seems to move, but when you turn to face it, all is still.
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur. Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
